e noted.', 'Synergism, Excretion', 'If possible, drugs that are potentially nephrotoxic including NSAIDs should be avoided during the 5 days of clofarabine administration.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/70181/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole', 'Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine', 1767369485);
